import React, { useState, useEffect } from 'react'; import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'; const Home = () => { const [mousePosition, setMousePosition] = useState({ x: 0, y: 0 }); const [scrollProgress, setScrollProgress] = useState(0); const [text, setText] = useState(''); const fullText = 'Crafting Stories Through Code & Design'; // Typing Animation Effect useEffect(() => { let index = 0; const timer = setInterval(() => { if (index <= fullText.length) { setText(fullText.slice(0, index)); index++; } else { clearInterval(timer); } }, 100); return () => clearInterval(timer); }, []); // Mouse Position Tracker useEffect(() => { const handleMouseMove = (e) => { setMousePosition({ x: e.clientX, y: e.clientY }); }; window.addEventListener('mousemove', handleMouseMove); return () => window.removeEventListener('mousemove', handleMouseMove); }, []); // Scroll Progress useEffect(() => { const handleScroll = () => { const totalHeight = document.documentElement.scrollHeight - window.innerHeight; const progress = (window.scrollY / totalHeight) * 100; setScrollProgress(progress); }; window.addEventListener('scroll', handleScroll); return () => window.removeEventListener('scroll', handleScroll); }, []); return (
